		I just tried a few things and doing the following works:
<denchmark-code>model2.Run(Fix(model1.Run(data), model2))

private static List<NamedOnnxValue> Fix(IDisposableReadOnlyCollection<DisposableNamedOnnxValue> t, InferenceSession model)
{
    var q = t.First().AsTensor<float>();
    var dims = q.Dimensions;
    var data = q.ToArray();
    var tensor = new DenseTensor<float>(data, dims);
    var name = model.InputMetadata.Keys.First();
    return new List<NamedOnnxValue> { NamedOnnxValue.CreateFromTensor(name, tensor) };
}
</denchmark-code>

So yes, both models work individually.

